~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : ppicture                                  ~FTPODnuts Revision
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : ppicture [<username>] [<picturefile>] 

   This command allows you to display an ascii picture to individual users.
   An error is displayed if you try to show a picture that does not exist.
   Also, typing .ppicture on its own will list out all available pictures.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : picture preview
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
